MATERIAL & CARE:
• Use a soft and slightly damp cloth to clean the body. Do not allow water or any other liquid to enter the straightener's openings.
  •  If you find any product or residue deposited on the plates, please take a damp paper napkin or a damp cotton cloth or a damp towel and gently clean the product or residue deposited on the plates.
  •  Do not try to clean or clear off any product or residue from the barrel when cold.
  •  Do not use any serum, liquid, detergent or anything except a bit of dampness (with water) to remove the residue or product deposits from the barrel.
  •  Do not scrub, scratch or try to file the surface of the barrel with any metal or plastic objects to clean or clear off any product or residue from the plates.
